# Spotify application Client ID — copy this file to `.env` and fill it in.
#
# This is the PUBLIC Client ID from your app at https://developer.spotify.com/dashboard.
# It is safe in client-side code with the Authorization Code + PKCE flow.
# Do NOT put the Client SECRET here or anywhere in this repo — PKCE does not use it.
#
# Register this exact redirect URI in the dashboard (must match what the app sends):
#   - Local dev:     http://127.0.0.1:5173/        (127.0.0.1, never localhost)
#   - GitHub Pages:  https://<user>.github.io/<repo>/
VITE_SPOTIFY_CLIENT_ID=
